title: Regent Wallet

creator: Regent Coin
descriptionHtml:
Regent Wallet is designed as a staking platform for Regent Coin.

Regent Wallet is designed for the convenience, cost effective solution and efficient time usage among the peer to peer community. Regent Coin is A UTILITY TOKEN, enables People to make their utility bill payments using the pay app.
descriptionShort: Revolutionize utility payments with Regent Coin - Convenient & efficient!
